The paper discusses the advancements in deep learning, specifically in the field of capsule networks. The proposed algorithm aims to improve the dynamic routing algorithm used in capsule networks, which is commonly used in computer vision tasks such as image classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of gradient propagation and the iterative process of routing, which are common topics in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) sub-categories.
